  "local_port": 53028,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How is Iphone 6s better than 6?",
  "response": "The iPhone 6s has several improvements over the iPhone 6. Here are some key enhancements:\n\n1. **3D Touch**: The iPhone 6s introduced 3D Touch, a pressure-sensitive technology that allows for new interactions with the display, like Peek and Pop for previews and shortcuts.\n\n2. **A9 Chip**: The 6s is equipped with the A9 chip, which is more powerful and efficient than the A8 chip in the iPhone 6. This results in better performance and battery life.\n\n3. **Camera Improvements**: The iPhone 6s has a 12-megapixel camera compared to the 8-megapixel camera on the iPhone 6. It also supports 4K video recording, Live Photos, and improved low-light performance.\n\n4. **Retina Flash**: The front-facing camera on the 6s includes a Retina Flash, which uses the display to provide a flash for selfies, improving their quality in low light.\n\n5. **Stronger Build**: The 6s uses a new aluminum alloy and a stronger cover glass, making it more durable. It also introduced the \"Series 7000 aluminum\" which is claimed to be stronger than the aluminum used in the iPhone 6.\n\n6. **Touch ID**: The Touch ID sensor in the 6s is second generation, which is faster and more responsive than the first-generation sensor in the iPhone 6.\n\n7. **Increased Storage Options**: The base model of the iPhone 6s came with 16GB of storage, but it also offered higher storage tiers up to 128GB. Later models started at 32GB.\n\n8. **Wi-Fi and LTE**: The iPhone 6s supports faster Wi-Fi (802.11ac with MIMO) and LTE (up to 300 Mbps) compared to the iPhone 6.\n\n9. **iOS Support**: The iPhone 6s was supported with iOS updates for a longer period than the iPhone 6, ensuring it received newer features and security updates for a more extended time.\n\nThese improvements make the iPhone 6s a more advanced and capable device compared to the iPhone 6.",
